      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. Widow woman must be a resident of Bihar.\n1. The woman should be a widow.\n1. The woman should be living below the poverty line.\n1. The annual income of the woman&#39;s family should be Rs. 60,000/- or less.\n1. The age of the woman should be 18 years or more.\n\n",
